    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras/252f9c6427fd7276fdd515e9193e202b.avif?t=1769311329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras_big/252f9c6427fd7276fdd515e9193e202b.avif?t=1769311329 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >备受好评的《Ala Mobile》在移动平台上赢得了超过 5000000 名玩家的喜爱，如今登陆 PC，为你带来快节奏（在支持的情况下最高可达 120+ FPS）、充满娱乐性的方程式赛车体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在来自世界各地的不同赛道上驾驶，并体验多种天气条件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经过 6 年的精心打磨，倾听了数千名玩家的反馈，为你呈现一款有趣且令人上瘾的方程式赛车游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras/7551c73adb1fc764cfe6af5dd09b3543.avif?t=1769311329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras_big/7551c73adb1fc764cfe6af5dd09b3543.avif?t=1769311329 width=800 height=421 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ala Mobile 从一开始就为你提供所需的一切。<br>强大的引擎？有。<br>完全可自定义的调校？有。<br>高效的减阻系统？有。<br>超车模式？有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赛车在赛车运动中非常重要，但<strong>车手永远更重要</strong>。按照你的喜好定制你的体验。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可自定义的锦标赛和比赛周末；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >计时赛排行榜；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线多人正面对战；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >周末轮胎分配与受限部件数量；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的损伤模型；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的故障系统；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >安全车介入；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由练习 1、2 和 3；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Q1、Q2 和 Q3；</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按照应有的方式驾驶：在 Windows 上支持方向盘并提供力反馈。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras/086096827c33a71a029ce7c0a7b73ee6.avif?t=1769311329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203370/extras_big/086096827c33a71a029ce7c0a7b73ee6.avif?t=1769311329 width=800 height=488 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >车辆和车手数据完全可自定义，赛车涂装和车手头盔同样如此！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两款强大的编辑器可让你从零开始创建涂装和头盔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还可以导入和导出项目与贴花，用于丰富编辑器，并与朋友分享你的创作！</p>",
